BT /F2 13 Tf 72 305.30 Td (V. Past International Action) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 280.65 Td (The international community has not been silent on Maintaining International Peace and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 266.15 Td (Security in Regions Affected by Protracted Armed Conflict. Earlier resolutions,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 251.65 Td (conferences, and frameworks have laid important groundwork, even if implementation has) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 237.15 Td (often fallen short of what was promised. Research which instruments are most relevant to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 222.65 Td (SC — including any prior actions taken by this committee or the bodies it answers to —) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 208.15 Td (and consider honestly why those efforts succeeded, stalled, or failed outright. A strong) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 193.65 Td (proposal builds on this record rather than ignoring it.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 72 166.10 Td (VI. Bloc Positions) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 141.45 Td (Delegations facing this topic generally fall into broader groupings shaped by geography,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 126.95 Td (level of development, historical experience, and strategic interest. Rather than) Tj ET
